    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support the decision to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 < 1.0 satisfies the primary acceptance criterion.",
